data.description: This impressive 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom 2-story home combines modern comfort with sustainable living. The property features xeriscaping, minimizing water usage and maintenance while enhancing curb appeal. Fully-fenced yard allows for privacy and pet-friendly spaces! Inside, the spacious living room welcomes you with ample natural light and a versatile layout, perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. The home boasts an abundance of storage options, including unfinished basement, wall to wall closet upstairs, and an extra large shed in back to keep your belongings organized. With its thoughtful design and eco-friendly landscaping, this home offers a harmonious blend of style and practicality, making it an ideal choice for those looking to embrace a sustainable lifestyle without compromising on space and convenience. All appliances stay including the washer and dryer. Call today to schedule your showing! Virtual Tour: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=RGPB3xPjLxV&mls=1
